SUBENT        G0102001   20251215   20260508   20260508       G059
BIB                 14         43
TITLE      Direct measurement of the 103Rh(n,g) and 103Rh(g,n)
            cross section up to stellar temperatures at the CSNS
            Back-n and SSRF SLEGS
AUTHOR     (Hao Liang, Zhen-Dong An, Wei Jiang, Zi-Rui Hao,
            Chen-Chen Guo, Yu-Gang Ma, Jie Ren, Xi-Chao Ruan,
            Jing-Yu Tang, Rui-Rui Fan, Gong-Tao Fan,
            Hong-Wei Wang, Wen-Qing Shen , Yu-Bing Li,
            Jun-Heng Hu, Di Sun, Ting Liu, Zi-Jun Liu, Yi Sui)
REFERENCE  (J,PL/B,872,140105,2026)
REL-REF    (O,32908001,Hao Liang+,J,PL/B,872,140105,2026)
            103Rh(n,g) dataset compiled separately
           (M,,H.Utsunomiya+,J,PR/C,109,014617,2024)
            Unfolding method
INSTITUTE  (3CPRIMP,3CPRSZH,3CPRFUD,3CPRIHP,3CPRARI,3CPRNRS,
            3CPRAEP,3CPRHST)
           (3CPRCPR) Spallation Neutron Source Science Center,
            Dongguan; Shenyang Normal University, Shenyang;
            University of South China, Hengyang; Guangxi Normal
            University, Guilin)
FACILITY   (ESTRG,3CPRARI) 3.5 GeV storage ring of Shanghai Laser
            Electron Gamma Source (SLEGS)
INC-SOURCE (LCS) 10.64 um CO2 laser photons scattered by 3.5 GeV
            electrons
SAMPLE     10 mm in diameter x 2.38 mm in thickness, 99.95% purity
DETECTOR   (HE3SP) flat efficiency detector (FED) consisting of
            26 3He proportional counters embedded in a
            polyethylene moderator (450 mm x 450 mm x 550 mm)
           (BGO) 76 mm x 200 mm, for measurement of gamma spectra
METHOD     (RINGR) for neutron detection efficiency determination
ANALYSIS   (UNFLD) unfolding with LCS photon energy profile
            measured by the BGO detector
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S) Statistical error
           (ERR-1) Methodological error
           . neutron count algorithm error
           . gamma-spectrum unfolding method error
           (ERR-2) Systematic error
           . FED efficiency error
           . BGO gamma spectrum error
           . target thickness error
           (ERR-T) Total error
STATUS     (APRVD) Proofread by Zirui Hao (2025-12-18)
HISTORY    (20251215R) Wang Jimin. Data received from Zirui Hao.
           (20251215C) On
